---
title: Roasted Curried Parsnips (V) with Cumin Bulgur Pilaf and Raisins
description: Parnsips are such a sweet and delicious vegetable and actually pretty diverse (they don’t just belong in a Sunday roast!). Who’d have thought coating them in curry powder and roasting them would make them such a great accompaniment to a bulgur pilaf!
